_sText:
To install this map, just go into C:\Programs(X86) Or Programs\Steam\Steamapps\Username\Counter-Strike Source\Cstrike\Maps and but the bsp file in there.

Please give me feedback and comment if you like it! A video will soon be uploaded to show you the map! Thanks for downloading!

[Click here for review of map](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vXw587pIRiA "")
